    "Body": " In this customer operations role, you will be required to build strong relationships with customers and maintain the company's image. Key Responsibilities \u2022 Responding promptly to user inquiries. \u2022 Management (escalation, monitoring and resolution) of user complaints. \u2022 Communicating with users through various channels \u2013 including LiveChat, Email, Skype and Telegram \u2022 Knowing our products inside and out so that you can answer questions. \u2022 Keeping statistics of customer interactions, transactions, comments and complaints. \u2022 Maintaining a positive, empathetic and professional attitude toward customers at all times. \u2022 Work closely with Operations, Technical and Community team to manage user expectations. Key Requirements \u2022 Intermediate Proficiency in both 1) English & Chinese language OR 2) Chinese & Vietnamese 3) English & Vietnamese is mandatory. Ability to speak a third language such as Vietnamese, Russian, Bahasa will be a strong added advantage. \u2022 Basic familiarity with financial trading terms, cryptocurrency trading and blockchain technology is preferred. \u2022 Ideally some prior experience in customer service, preferably in cryptocurrency exchange or financial services. Nevertheless, training will be provided (Candidates with no prior experience but with a customer service aptitude will be considered) \u2022 Familiar with the use of community and social media tools e.g. Telegram \u2022 Good team player and able to adapt to different cultures. Able to work under stress and deliver on a time-sensitive basis. \u2022 Singapore citizen, permanent residents preferred. Job Type Contract/Internship \u2013 6 months New graduates or student interns with strong interest or experience in blockchain technology or cryptocurrency trading are welcome to apply. The cryptocurrency market is growing exponentially. There is no better place to learn about blockchain technology and financial trading than in a digital asset exchange. This is a fast-paced environment. The culture is demanding but if you are confident and have a can-do attitude the potential rewards are significant. Skills Crypto Trading knowledge, Multilingual Compensation Negotiable ", 
